original_title: UFC Fight Night 135: Gaethje vs. Vick
overview: UFC Fight Night 135: Gaethje vs. Vick was a mixed martial arts event produced by the Ultimate Fighting Championship that was held on August 25, 2018 at Pinnacle Bank Arena in Lincoln, Nebraska, United States. A lightweight bout between former WSOF Lightweight Champion Justin Gaethje and James Vick served as the event headliner.
title: UFC Fight Night 135: Gaethje vs. Vick
